{
  "id": "5bab1fbbbb72e70013e5e1b0",
  "title": "問題解決大全",
  "created": 1537941451,
  "updated": 1555909527,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5bab1fcbaff09e0000f220ae",
      "text": "問題解決大全",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941451,
      "updated": 1537941473
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab1fcdaff09e0000f220af",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/9ec2c853b9e5bdd4a57149d3767d5e27]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941453,
      "updated": 1537941453
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab1fbbbb72e70013e5e1b0",
      "text": "\t問題解決大全――ビジネスや人生のハードルを乗り越える37のツール",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941451,
      "updated": 1537941474
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab1fe2aff09e0000f220b0",
      "text": "\t[読書猿]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941474,
      "updated": 1537941487
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2000aff09e0000f220b2",
      "text": " [Amazon https://amzn.to/2N5gNyp]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941504,
      "updated": 1537941507
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac76aeaff09e0000dda8c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029230,
      "updated": 1538029230
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2003aff09e0000f220b3",
      "text": "とても良い本、しかし歯ごたえもあるので普通の書籍のように頭から1回読んで終わる本ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941508,
      "updated": 1555909519
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd4b8eaff09e00000c85d8",
      "text": "\t[咀嚼すべき本]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555909519,
      "updated": 1555909521
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac76b2aff09e0000dda8c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029234,
      "updated": 1538029234
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2026aff09e0000f220b4",
      "text": "\t【[リニアな問題解決]】 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941543,
      "updated": 1537941630
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220c5",
      "text": "\t\t直線的な因果性を基礎に置く問題解決法。 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1537941633
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220c6",
      "text": "\t\t因果関係を直線的に遡り、たどり着いた究極原因を除去・変化させることで、結果を変え、問題を解決する。 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1537941633
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220c7",
      "text": "\t【[サーキュラーな問題解決]】 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1537941633
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220c8",
      "text": "\t\t[鶏と卵]の関係のように、原因と結果の関係がループしている場合に用いる問題解決法。 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1537941633
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220c9",
      "text": "\t\t究極原因の除去・変化ではなく、問題へ対する認知を変える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1537941633
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2075aff09e0000f220d4",
      "text": "\t\t悪循環に変化をもたらし、間接的に問題を変える。 ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941622,
      "updated": 1537941633
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7729aff09e0000dda8c4",
      "text": "  [nishio.icon][システム思考]と関連している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029353,
      "updated": 1538029365
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7806aff09e0000dda8d2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029574,
      "updated": 1538029574
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac774baff09e0000dda8c5",
      "text": "7/37は青リンクになったが、赤リンクのものも掘り下げてみると色々なページとつながる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029387,
      "updated": 1538029597
    },
    {
      "id": "5cbd4b97aff09e00000c85d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555909527,
      "updated": 1555909527
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2093aff09e0000f220d5",
      "text": "\tリニア",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941652,
      "updated": 1538029389
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac774faff09e0000dda8c6",
      "text": " \t問題の認知",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029391,
      "updated": 1538029394
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220ca",
      "text": "  \t01 [100 年ルール]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1538029401
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac78aeaff09e0000dda8d6",
      "text": "   \t「100年後にも重要なことか？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029743,
      "updated": 1538029749
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2097aff09e0000f220d6",
      "text": "   02 [ニーバーの仕分け]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941655,
      "updated": 1538029401
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac78ceaff09e0000dda8d7",
      "text": "   \t問題が大きいままだと何を変えたら良いかわかりにくいので、分割して[可変度]を評価する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029775,
      "updated": 1538029848
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab209aaff09e0000f220d7",
      "text": "   03 [ノミナル・グループ・プロセス]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941659,
      "updated": 1538029401
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7940aff09e0000dda8d8",
      "text": "   \t[ブレインストーミング]と[ブレインライティング]を元に1970年代に開発された手法",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029888,
      "updated": 1538029913
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab209faff09e0000f220d8",
      "text": "   04 [キャメロット]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941663,
      "updated": 1538029401
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac798daff09e0000dda8d9",
      "text": "   \t何が[問題]かがわからない時、[理想状態]を考えて、現実とのギャップを考える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029966,
      "updated": 1538029990
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac782aaff09e0000dda8d4",
      "text": "   \t[問題はあるべき姿と現状のギャップ]は[ハーバート・サイモン]の[意思決定の科学]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029611,
      "updated": 1538029679
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20a2aff09e0000f220d9",
      "text": "   05 [佐藤の問題構造図式] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941666,
      "updated": 1538029401
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac79f0aff09e0000dda8db",
      "text": "   \t取り組む必要がある課題はギャップの解消が容易ではない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030064,
      "updated": 1538030076
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac79deaff09e0000dda8da",
      "text": "   \tギャップの解消ができない原因を列挙した後、テンプレートに従って整理する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030046,
      "updated": 1538030117
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20a7aff09e0000f220da",
      "text": "   06 [ティンバーゲンの4 つの問い]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941672,
      "updated": 1538029401
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7ad4aff09e0000dda8dd",
      "text": "   \t「なぜ」に4種類あるという主張",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030292,
      "updated": 1538030306
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7a44aff09e0000dda8dc",
      "text": "   \t僕の[4種類のなぜ]と、一部同じ、一部違う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030149,
      "updated": 1538030326
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20aeaff09e0000f220db",
      "text": "   07 [ロジック・ツリー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941678,
      "updated": 1538029401
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7b19aff09e0000dda8df",
      "text": "   \t[なぜなぜ分析]と関連している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030362,
      "updated": 1538030369
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7b20aff09e0000dda8e0",
      "text": "    「なぜ」を掘り下げていった[why-whyツリー] [診断ツリー]と",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030369,
      "updated": 1538030417
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7b50aff09e0000dda8e2",
      "text": "    howを掘り下げていった [how-howツリー] [解決ツリー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030417,
      "updated": 1538030417
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7b74aff09e0000dda8e3",
      "text": "    関連: [なぜを掘り下げる＆どうやって目標達成するか]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030452,
      "updated": 1538030454
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7c4faff09e0000dda8e5",
      "text": "    今世の中で使われている「ロジックツリー」なる言葉はロジカルでないという指摘",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030671,
      "updated": 1538030704
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5cc59aff09e00009d6a60",
      "text": "    \t→同様のものが[イシューツリー]と呼ばれている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555418202,
      "updated": 1555418221
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5cc99aff09e00009d6a61",
      "text": "   \t[原因と結果がループしている]場合、ツリーを伸ばしていると上位のものが下位に再び現れる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555418265,
      "updated": 1555418311
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ccd6aff09e00009d6a63",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t[因果ループ図](→326ページ)や[現状分析ツリー](→314ページ)を用いるべき",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555418326,
      "updated": 1555418335
    },
    {
      "id": "5cb5ccc7aff09e00009d6a62",
      "text": "   08 [特性要因図]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1555418311,
      "updated": 1555418326
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7c27aff09e0000dda8e4",
      "text": "   \t特性(結果)は直接コントロールできない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538030632,
      "updated": 1538030646
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac775caff09e0000dda8c7",
      "text": " \t解決策の探求",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029404,
      "updated": 1538029412
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20b5aff09e0000f220dd",
      "text": "   09 [文献調査]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941686,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20b8aff09e0000f220de",
      "text": "   10 [力まかせ探索] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941689,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220cd",
      "text": "   11 [フェルミ推定]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20c0aff09e0000f220df",
      "text": "   12 [マインドマップ](R)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941697,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20c6aff09e0000f220e0",
      "text": "   13 [ブレインライティング]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941702,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20caaff09e0000f220e1",
      "text": "   14 [コンセプトマップ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941706,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20ceaff09e0000f220e2",
      "text": "   15 [KJ法] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941711,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220ce",
      "text": "   16 [お山の大将]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20daaff09e0000f220e3",
      "text": "   17 [フランクリンの功罪表]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941726,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20ddaff09e0000f220e4",
      "text": "   18 [機会費用]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941726,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20e1aff09e0000f220e5",
      "text": "   19 [ケプナー・トリゴーの決定分析]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941729,
      "updated": 1538029427
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7777aff09e0000dda8c8",
      "text": "\t\t解決策の実行",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029431,
      "updated": 1538029434
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20e5aff09e0000f220e6",
      "text": "   20 [ぐずぐず主義克服シート] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941733,
      "updated": 1538029439
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220cf",
      "text": "   21 [過程決定計画図]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1538029439
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20eeaff09e0000f220e7",
      "text": "   22 [オデュッセウスの鎖]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941742,
      "updated": 1538029439
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20f1aff09e0000f220e8",
      "text": "   23 [行動デザインシート]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941746,
      "updated": 1538029439
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7780aff09e0000dda8c9",
      "text": "  結果の吟味",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029440,
      "updated": 1538029445
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20f5aff09e0000f220e9",
      "text": "   24 [セルフモニタリング]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941749,
      "updated": 1538029452
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab20f9aff09e0000f220ea",
      "text": "   25 [問題解決のタイムライン] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941753,
      "updated": 1538029452
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab206caff09e0000f220d0",
      "text": "   26 [フロイドの解き直し]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941613,
      "updated": 1538029452
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac778daff09e0000dda8ca",
      "text": "\tサーキュラー",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029453,
      "updated": 1538029456
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac7798aff09e0000dda8cb",
      "text": " \t問題の認知",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029465,
      "updated": 1538029467
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2101aff09e0000f220eb",
      "text": "   27 [ミラクル・クエスチョン]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941762,
      "updated": 1538029471
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2105aff09e0000f220ec",
      "text": "   28 [推論の梯子]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941765,
      "updated": 1538029471
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2108aff09e0000f220ed",
      "text": "   29 [リフレーミング]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941768,
      "updated": 1538029471
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab210baff09e0000f220ee",
      "text": "   30 [問題への相談]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941771,
      "updated": 1538029471
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab210eaff09e0000f220ef",
      "text": "   31 [現状分析ツリー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941774,
      "updated": 1538029471
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2114aff09e0000f220f0",
      "text": "   32 [因果ループ図]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941780,
      "updated": 1538029471
    },
    {
      "id": "5bac77a0aff09e0000dda8cc",
      "text": "  解決策の探求",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1538029473,
      "updated": 1538029477
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab2117aff09e0000f220f1",
      "text": "   33 [スケーリング・クエスチョン]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941784,
      "updated": 1538029479
    },
    {
      "id": "5bab211baff09e0000f220f2",
      "text": "   34 [エスノグラフィー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1537941788,
      "updated": 1538029479
    },
    {
